Titolo: Arcade Spirits

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Arcade Spirits is a dating sim visual novel game released in 2019 for Windows and in 2020 for PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch, and Xbox One. It was developed by Fiction Factory Games and published by PQube. It is set in an alternate history where the video game crash of 1983 never happened, leading to arcades to continue being successful. Players control a customizable character who can be female, male, or non-binary, and can choose whether they want to approach the seven romance candidates romantically or platonically.

